<h4>

A Legacy of Swing

</h4>

<p>

Founded by Doug Wareing, Jazz House Big Band has brought authentic big band music to audiences throughout Eastern Idaho for nearly three decades.

</p>

<p>

Featuring a full eighteen-piece ensemble, the band performs classics from Glenn Miller, Count Basie, Duke Ellington, Benny Goodman, and many more.

</p>

<p>

Whether entertaining at weddings, galas, community concerts, festivals, or private events, the Jazz House Big Band continues to preserve America's greatest music while inspiring future generations of jazz musicians.

</p>

